<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="16500000t" end="54600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">我到底是被卷进什么事了</p>
<p begin="67500000t" end="108300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">我父亲从小被当作大集团的长男来教养</p>
<p begin="108300000t" end="129200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">但他舍弃家族地位独立出来</p>
<p begin="129200000t" end="148300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">自己开了一间日本料亭</p>
<p begin="155000000t" end="168900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">某天</p>
<p begin="168900000t" end="196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">我爸出了一个奇怪的题目</p>
<p begin="196000000t" end="227600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">莉音 你代替我处理吧</p>
<p begin="227600000t" end="271000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">爸爸说要让我们了解犯罪必遭报应</p>
<p begin="271000000t" end="321400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">恐怕是知道什么关于妈妈命案的内情</p>
<p begin="331000000t" end="355300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">如果你得到优先选择权</p>
<p begin="355300000t" end="379500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">拿到的遗产就随你处置</p>
<p begin="473200000t" end="496700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="496700000t" end="525000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="525000000t" end="547500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="547500000t" end="575900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="575900000t" end="598500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="598500000t" end="626700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="626700000t" end="649300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="649300000t" end="677600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="677600000t" end="729800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="729800000t" end="764000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="764000000t" end="803700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="819000000t" end="863200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="863200000t" end="917000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="917000000t" end="965400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="965400000t" end="994300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="994300000t" end="1028400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="1056800000t" end="1095100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">我没有亲人遭谋杀身亡的实感</p>
<p begin="1095100000t" end="1135600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">以及证明祖父就是那起事件凶手的课题</p>
<p begin="1135600000t" end="1167800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">还有巨额遗产都让我觉得莫名其妙</p>
<p begin="1173500000t" end="1200300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">而且我还穿着便服就来了</p>
<p begin="1200300000t" end="1229800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">各位辛苦了</p>
<p begin="1229800000t" end="1244800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">或许你们会很疑惑</p>
<p begin="1244800000t" end="1272900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">我是谁 为什么在这里</p>
<p begin="1272900000t" end="1294600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">对我抱持戒心</p>
<p begin="1294600000t" end="1317100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不过请各位想想</p>
<p begin="1317100000t" end="1340900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">最困扰的其实是我</p>
<p begin="1340900000t" end="1366200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我可是彻头彻尾的局外人</p>
<p begin="1366200000t" end="1387100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">却被要求负责这么诡异的工作</p>
<p begin="1387100000t" end="1418400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">空出时间大老远跑来这里</p>
<p begin="1418400000t" end="1448800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">各位或许认为不愿意的话可以拒绝</p>
<p begin="1449300000t" end="1478400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">但有谁能拒绝那位音无董事长的要求呢</p>
<p begin="1478400000t" end="1509700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">而且他要求我对各位评分排名</p>
<p begin="1509700000t" end="1544300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">被排在后面的人肯定会讨厌我</p>
<p begin="1544300000t" end="1582800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">天晓得之后我会受到什么样的报复</p>
<p begin="1582800000t" end="1614900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">不 再怎么说也没那么心胸狭窄</p>
<p begin="1614900000t" end="1634000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">爸爸也不可能让我们那么做的</p>
<p begin="1634000000t" end="1670000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">但要是有人等董事长过世再来算账 我会很困扰的</p>
<p begin="1670000000t" end="1697800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">说是这样说 董事长还健在</p>
<p begin="1697800000t" end="1725300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我若没完成职责会惹他不高兴的</p>
<p begin="1725300000t" end="1745000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">这样下去无论结果如何</p>
<p begin="1745000000t" end="1765900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">我都只有吃亏的份</p>
<p begin="1765900000t" end="1805500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">那岩永小姐你怎么会被祖父选上?</p>
<p begin="1822500000t" end="1855900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">两位是否对我做过身家调查了呢?</p>
<p begin="1855900000t" end="1875200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我有试过</p>
<p begin="1875200000t" end="1910200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">但值得信任的征信社全都拒绝了</p>
<p begin="1910200000t" end="1923100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">就这一点看来</p>
<p begin="1923100000t" end="1947200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我明白你是个很特别的人物</p>
<p begin="1947200000t" end="1961100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">我的话是</p>
<p begin="1961100000t" end="1993600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">外甥碰巧在高中时和你参加同一个社团</p>
<p begin="1993600000t" end="2024000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">你还记得天地学这个人吗</p>
<p begin="2024000000t" end="2051900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">哎呀 原来您是社长的亲戚呀</p>
<p begin="2051900000t" end="2088300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">他还忠告我绝对别与你为敌呢</p>
<p begin="2119100000t" end="2129600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">总之</p>
<p begin="2129600000t" end="2163400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">是因为有流言在我不知道的地方传了开来</p>
<p begin="2163400000t" end="2190900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">音无董事长才会看上我的样子</p>
<p begin="2195500000t" end="2206200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">先不说这个</p>
<p begin="2206200000t" end="2239600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">我可不希望因为这件事被任何人怨恨</p>
<p begin="2239600000t" end="2273800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">这位九郎学长其实也不是我的随从</p>
<p begin="2273800000t" end="2302200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">而是我从高中开始交往的情人</p>
<p begin="2302200000t" end="2314700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">情人?</p>
<p begin="2314700000t" end="2350600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">难得能和情人一起住进不错的旅馆</p>
<p begin="2350600000t" end="2380600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">当然希望能好好享受一下啊</p>
<p begin="2380600000t" end="2416800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">董事长帮我们准备的套房浴室也很宽广</p>
<p begin="2416800000t" end="2439000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我们要一起入浴做洗壶</p>
<p begin="2439000000t" end="2456200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">然后再这样那样…</p>
<p begin="2480800000t" end="2511900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">失礼了 不小心暴露太多个人欲望</p>
<p begin="2511900000t" end="2527800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">不过我想各位</p>
<p begin="2527800000t" end="2566200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">也不想到明天都勾心斗角 疑神疑鬼的吧</p>
<p begin="2566200000t" end="2580400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">就是说啊</p>
<p begin="2580400000t" end="2611700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">亲戚之间因此搞坏关系太没意义了</p>
<p begin="2616200000t" end="2638000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">所以大家来协商吧</p>
<p begin="2638000000t" end="2649700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">协商?</p>
<p begin="2657200000t" end="2674300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">董事长的要求</p>
<p begin="2674300000t" end="2724800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">是证明他在23年前杀死音无澄女士</p>
<p begin="2724800000t" end="2742300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">那么不如大家一起讨论</p>
<p begin="2742300000t" end="2768500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">汇整出董事长想要的答案吧</p>
<p begin="2768500000t" end="2810200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">也请各位先商量好遗产的分配方式</p>
<p begin="2810200000t" end="2833600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">让我依照大家都能如愿的方式</p>
<p begin="2833600000t" end="2857700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">向董事长报告结果</p>
<p begin="2858100000t" end="2901600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">假装是按符合最终解答的程度来决定排名</p>
<p begin="2907400000t" end="2953200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">老实说 分别听你们的答案太麻烦了</p>
<p begin="2953200000t" end="2977000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">我先离席约一个小时</p>
<p begin="2977000000t" end="3015500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">请各位在这期间讨论一下我的提议吧</p>
<p begin="3075500000t" end="3101800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你们觉得这个提议是爸爸安排的</p>
<p begin="3101800000t" end="3123800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">还是岩永大小姐擅自提出的?</p>
<p begin="3123800000t" end="3161000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">我是不认为她能无视董事长的想法行动啦</p>
<p begin="3161000000t" end="3193100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">但感觉那位大小姐很可能做得出来</p>
<p begin="3193100000t" end="3224300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">反正提议本身并不坏</p>
<p begin="3224300000t" end="3240600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">道理也说得通</p>
<p begin="3247700000t" end="3271100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">遗产的部分 你们有什么想法</p>
<p begin="3271100000t" end="3310700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">我个人有想保留的资产和权利</p>
<p begin="3310700000t" end="3329100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">只要能保证把那部分留给我</p>
<p begin="3329100000t" end="3354500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">这次的课题排第几名我都无所谓</p>
<p begin="3354500000t" end="3373200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">薰子姐姐的想法呢</p>
<p begin="3373200000t" end="3428000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">薰子说她不希望让亮马先生 以及晋先生你单方面得利</p>
<p begin="3428000000t" end="3466200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">你对集团有贡献 董事长很器重你</p>
<p begin="3466200000t" end="3483000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">亮马先生则是完全相反</p>
<p begin="3483300000t" end="3497500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">贯彻自己的道路</p>
<p begin="3497500000t" end="3519300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">这点也受董事长赏识</p>
<p begin="3519300000t" end="3571800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">相较之下薰子似乎觉得父亲不怎么爱她</p>
<p begin="3571800000t" end="3606400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">如果在继承上也是两位受到优待</p>
<p begin="3606400000t" end="3628600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">她恐怕会很气愤</p>
<p begin="3628600000t" end="3674400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">姐姐只是想要赢过我和哥哥获得满足感啊</p>
<p begin="3674400000t" end="3697700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">亮马先生对遗产有什么想法</p>
<p begin="3697700000t" end="3721600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">这根本用不着问</p>
<p begin="3721600000t" end="3745400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">他肯定是说大笔遗产只会引来麻烦</p>
<p begin="3745400000t" end="3786600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">如果莉音有想要的东西就随她高兴吧</p>
<p begin="3786600000t" end="3816700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">叔叔 既然你这么了解我爸</p>
<p begin="3816700000t" end="3838300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">为什么你们到现在关系还那么差啊</p>
<p begin="3838300000t" end="3855800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">就是因为了解才处不来</p>
<p begin="3855800000t" end="3888700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">哥哥老是做我看不惯的事</p>
<p begin="3888700000t" end="3913800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">无论是长男放弃继承</p>
<p begin="3913800000t" end="3933800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">还是我分到特别多遗产</p>
<p begin="3933800000t" end="3948500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">都会引起周遭臆测</p>
<p begin="3948500000t" end="3982300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">肯定会有人说我在幕后搞鬼</p>
<p begin="3982300000t" end="4023100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">也不想想我得花多少心力处理这些事</p>
<p begin="4023100000t" end="4053600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">反正哥哥只要能做自己想做的事就满足了</p>
<p begin="4053600000t" end="4072400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">总觉得很不好意思</p>
<p begin="4081800000t" end="4111600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">是哥哥不好 不是莉音你的错啦</p>
<p begin="4111900000t" end="4146200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">那顺序就让耕也姑丈排第一</p>
<p begin="4146200000t" end="4166900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">给薰子姑姑面子</p>
<p begin="4166900000t" end="4181900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">要继承什么</p>
<p begin="4181900000t" end="4227000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">则由晋叔叔和耕也姑丈你们讨论最好吧?</p>
<p begin="4227000000t" end="4249500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">我排第几都无所谓</p>
<p begin="4249500000t" end="4291200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我只要能让薰子满足就没有意见</p>
<p begin="4291200000t" end="4300800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">晋先生呢?</p>
<p begin="4300800000t" end="4331300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">与其竞争谁的答案比较优秀</p>
<p begin="4331300000t" end="4354300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">这种融洽的方式简单多了</p>
<p begin="4354300000t" end="4383800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">而且我本来就不想象这样争夺遗产</p>
<p begin="4383800000t" end="4403100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">那就这么办吧</p>
<p begin="4403100000t" end="4410100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">嗯</p>
<p begin="4410100000t" end="4417300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">好的</p>
<p begin="4417300000t" end="4439800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">感觉好怪呢</p>
<p begin="4439800000t" end="4456100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">明明事关巨额遗产</p>
<p begin="4456100000t" end="4478600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">却一下子就圆满解决了</p>
<p begin="4487300000t" end="4524400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">说到底 这个题目真的有正确答案吗</p>
<p begin="4532700000t" end="4548100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">如果祖父真的是凶手</p>
<p begin="4548100000t" end="4581900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">想要揭发自己的罪行以求赎罪</p>
<p begin="4581900000t" end="4614500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">他自己说明犯案方式比较快吧</p>
<p begin="4614500000t" end="4647900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">为什么要特地叫我们想原因?</p>
<p begin="4647900000t" end="4677500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">是不是这个题目背后还有其他目的呢</p>
<p begin="4677500000t" end="4706700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">祖父知道一些很特殊的内情</p>
<p begin="4706700000t" end="4725500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">只有现在才能说明</p>
<p begin="4725500000t" end="4749300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">他或许是想让我们注意到这点</p>
<p begin="4749300000t" end="4765500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">我爸是这么说的</p>
<p begin="4771300000t" end="4794700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">看来就算要答应岩永大小姐的提议</p>
<p begin="4794700000t" end="4818800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">还是得先问清一些事呢</p>
<p begin="4818800000t" end="4841000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">各位想太多了</p>
<p begin="4841000000t" end="4871400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">音无董事长与澄女士的死有关连</p>
<p begin="4871400000t" end="4900200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">但就算他亲自说明杀害方式</p>
<p begin="4900200000t" end="4918900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">你们大概也不会相信</p>
<p begin="4925600000t" end="4961200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">他才决定要让你们自己找出答案</p>
<p begin="4961200000t" end="4983700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">你这话不是骗人的吗</p>
<p begin="4983700000t" end="4998700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">这题目是有答案的</p>
<p begin="4998700000t" end="5038700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">只要各位追求真相 就能找到答案</p>
<p begin="5038700000t" end="5071200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">可是爸爸没有任何可疑之处啊</p>
<p begin="5071200000t" end="5087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">真的是那样吗</p>
<p begin="5087000000t" end="5103000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">比方说在命案发生时</p>
<p begin="5103000000t" end="5136590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">音无董事长不希望被当作嫌犯的相关人士</p>
<p begin="5136590000t" end="5165390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">也就是亮马先生 薰子小姐 晋先生</p>
<p begin="5165390000t" end="5188800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">还有耕也先生所有人都有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="5188800000t" end="5204700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">这点就挺可疑的吧</p>
<p begin="5204700000t" end="5234800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">简直像是为了保护你们刻意安排的</p>
<p begin="5234800000t" end="5277300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">当时能办到这点的只有音无董事长了吧?</p>
<p begin="5289800000t" end="5321900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">命案发生在23年前的2月18日</p>
<p begin="5321900000t" end="5341100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">晚上7点左右</p>
<p begin="5341100000t" end="5363600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">澄女士当时58岁</p>
<p begin="5363600000t" end="5396200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">她独自前往个人经营的按摩店</p>
<p begin="5396200000t" end="5417800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">这是她每个月一次的休息时间</p>
<p begin="5417800000t" end="5436200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">是完全私人的行程</p>
<p begin="5436200000t" end="5468700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">她从不依靠车子接送 都是自行前往</p>
<p begin="5468700000t" end="5502500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">并在回程的路上遭到不明人士袭击</p>
<p begin="5502500000t" end="5515400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">抢劫啊</p>
<p begin="5515400000t" end="5532100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">谁来抓住那个男人</p>
<p begin="5541200000t" end="5573400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">抓住那个穿黑色外套的男人</p>
<p begin="5573400000t" end="5586300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">他往车站跑了</p>
<p begin="5586300000t" end="5616300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">听见叫声的居民们赶到现场时</p>
<p begin="5616300000t" end="5640100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">澄女士已经断气了</p>
<p begin="5640100000t" end="5657300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">身体还有余温</p>
<p begin="5657300000t" end="5675100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">能推断命案刚发生不久</p>
<p begin="5675100000t" end="5708900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">死因是心脏附近被刀子刺了两次</p>
<p begin="5708900000t" end="5727300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">造成出血性休克死亡</p>
<p begin="5727300000t" end="5769500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">查不到刀子的来历 也验不出指纹</p>
<p begin="5769500000t" end="5802000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">澄女士习惯随身携带大笔现金</p>
<p begin="5802000000t" end="5831500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">钱包里总是装着一百万以上</p>
<p begin="5831500000t" end="5859000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">案发当下纸币全被拿走了</p>
<p begin="5864000000t" end="5902100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">乍看之下是起强盗杀人的单纯案件</p>
<p begin="5902100000t" end="5951200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">犯人抢现金时遭受反抗便顺势刺杀被害者</p>
<p begin="5951200000t" end="5970400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">状况看起来是如此</p>
<p begin="5970400000t" end="5998400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">然而由于找不到更多线索</p>
<p begin="5998400000t" end="6020000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">调查马上陷入胶着状态</p>
<p begin="6020000000t" end="6054200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">警方一边当作强盗杀人进行调查</p>
<p begin="6054200000t" end="6111900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">同时也考虑是如此伪装的谋杀之可能性</p>
<p begin="6111900000t" end="6152300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">因为澄女士在工作方面受到许多人怨恨</p>
<p begin="6152300000t" end="6187400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">另外家人们和耕也先生也各有动机</p>
<p begin="6187400000t" end="6240300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">各位全都知道澄女士 每个月会去一次按摩店</p>
<p begin="6240300000t" end="6275300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">都有办法计划在她回程中埋伏袭击</p>
<p begin="6280000000t" end="6311200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">她反对薰子小姐和耕也先生的婚事</p>
<p begin="6311200000t" end="6338700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">阻挠亮马先生和晋先生规划未来</p>
<p begin="6338700000t" end="6352500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">音无董事长则是</p>
<p begin="6352500000t" end="6386600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">担心孩子们的困境和集团面临的危机</p>
<p begin="6386600000t" end="6417200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">每个人都有将澄女士视为阻碍的理由</p>
<p begin="6417200000t" end="6437500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">当时我和哥哥</p>
<p begin="6437500000t" end="6466700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">的确都抱着要是妈妈消失该有多好的想法</p>
<p begin="6466700000t" end="6501900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">她完全不把我放在眼里</p>
<p begin="6501900000t" end="6521000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">还威胁我要是不跟薰子分手</p>
<p begin="6521000000t" end="6561400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">就要毁掉我刚起步的事业</p>
<p begin="6561400000t" end="6585700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">叫我不心怀杀意也难</p>
<p begin="6585700000t" end="6611100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">然而各位都有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="6611100000t" end="6632700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">很快就被排除了嫌疑</p>
<p begin="6632700000t" end="6655200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">音无董事长人在其他县</p>
<p begin="6655200000t" end="6693300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">晚间7点左右正与10几个人开会</p>
<p begin="6693300000t" end="6710000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">亮马先生和晋先生都在</p>
<p begin="6710000000t" end="6746600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">距离命案现场开车1小时的集团总公司</p>
<p begin="6746600000t" end="6792200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">命案发生时被人目击两人在公司里吵架</p>
<p begin="6792200000t" end="6815000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">当时我们都还年轻</p>
<p begin="6815000000t" end="6848500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">我才20几岁 哥哥也才刚过30</p>
<p begin="6848500000t" end="6893500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">哥哥虽然瞒着妈妈去名店学习厨艺</p>
<p begin="6893500000t" end="6924400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">但被妈妈逮到 强迫他回总公司上班</p>
<p begin="6924400000t" end="6945100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">让他累积了很多压力</p>
<p begin="6945100000t" end="6975700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">我则是只被交付辅佐哥哥的工作</p>
<p begin="6975700000t" end="6991100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">也感到非常不满</p>
<p begin="6991100000t" end="7014500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">哥哥工作得不情不愿</p>
<p begin="7014500000t" end="7042400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">我则是想要那些工作却得不到</p>
<p begin="7042400000t" end="7066200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">这使我们动不动就为了小事起冲突</p>
<p begin="7066200000t" end="7116200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">据说周遭都知道你们关系不好</p>
<p begin="7116200000t" end="7148700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">但那天是第一次在公司里大打出手</p>
<p begin="7148700000t" end="7175000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">所以才成了两位不在场的铁证</p>
<p begin="7175000000t" end="7202500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">这要说是偶然 也真是太巧了呢</p>
<p begin="7288500000t" end="7330100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">(无法反抗的孩子们)</p>
<p begin="7334400000t" end="7346000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">耕也先生也是</p>
<p begin="7346000000t" end="7372300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">据说命案发生时人在跑业务</p>
<p begin="7372300000t" end="7411100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">为了交涉完全抽不开身呢</p>
<p begin="7411100000t" end="7436100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">我当时33岁</p>
<p begin="7436100000t" end="7462400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">没有任何靠山 到哪都会吃闭门羹</p>
<p begin="7462400000t" end="7493700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">所以苦苦纠缠客户可是家常便饭</p>
<p begin="7493700000t" end="7501500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">是啊</p>
<p begin="7501500000t" end="7534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">多亏如此你的不在场证明牢不可破</p>
<p begin="7534000000t" end="7557100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">要是吃了闭门羹就干脆离开</p>
<p begin="7557100000t" end="7591200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">说不定就有办法去命案现场了呢</p>
<p begin="7591200000t" end="7620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">果然平常就该努力工作</p>
<p begin="7620000000t" end="7642900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">薰子小姐因为弄伤左脚</p>
<p begin="7642900000t" end="7664700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">于是取消当天的行程</p>
<p begin="7664700000t" end="7691700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">一个人待在耕也先生的公寓休息</p>
<p begin="7691700000t" end="7706300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">薰子那天白天</p>
<p begin="7706300000t" end="7735500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">似乎在公寓的门口狠狠摔了一跤</p>
<p begin="7735500000t" end="7752600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">虽然让她待在房里休息</p>
<p begin="7752600000t" end="7773500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">但到了傍晚脚肿得很严重</p>
<p begin="7773500000t" end="7800700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">我半夜带她去医院</p>
<p begin="7800700000t" end="7828600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">才发现她左脚小腿骨折</p>
<p begin="7828600000t" end="7846100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">就直接让她住院了</p>
<p begin="7846100000t" end="7867000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">因为这个意外</p>
<p begin="7867000000t" end="7892700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">薰子小姐才得以解除嫌疑</p>
<p begin="7892700000t" end="7921200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">因为警方判断她脚伤严重 不可能袭击并杀害澄女士</p>
<p begin="7921200000t" end="7944600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">才被排除了嫌疑</p>
<p begin="7944600000t" end="7960800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">还真是幸运呢</p>
<p begin="7968300000t" end="7995900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">岩永小姐 你到底想说什么</p>
<p begin="8005900000t" end="8067500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">就算要证明祖父挑大家 有不在场证明的时候杀害祖母</p>
<p begin="8067500000t" end="8087500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">你的说法不会太恶劣了吗</p>
<p begin="8087500000t" end="8104200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">简直像在暗示除了薰子姑姑以外</p>
<p begin="8104200000t" end="8126700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">大家都知道祖父的犯罪计划</p>
<p begin="8126700000t" end="8173500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">刻意在命案时间制造不在场证明一样</p>
<p begin="8173500000t" end="8184400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">怎么会呢</p>
<p begin="8184400000t" end="8206400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我可不会做那么没品的事</p>
<p begin="8206400000t" end="8236400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">我的确提议了要各位私下协商</p>
<p begin="8236400000t" end="8262400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">但各位再怎么无欲无求好了</p>
<p begin="8262400000t" end="8292400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">我也没料到你们竟然这么快就能达成共识</p>
<p begin="8292700000t" end="8329500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">毕竟遗产金额惊人 也与集团经营有关</p>
<p begin="8329500000t" end="8367100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">实际拥有继承权的薰子小姐 和亮马先生都没到场</p>
<p begin="8367100000t" end="8385800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">还以为各位会再观察一下状况呢</p>
<p begin="8385800000t" end="8417800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">简直就像是各位都有不为人知的问题</p>
<p begin="8417800000t" end="8444600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">想在事情闹大前快点解决一样</p>
<p begin="8444600000t" end="8479700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">协商其实也违反了音无董事长的希望</p>
<p begin="8479700000t" end="8494200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">若不是心里有鬼</p>
<p begin="8494200000t" end="8523800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">应该会更真诚地面对这个课题吧</p>
<p begin="8530500000t" end="8559200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">大家都有不在场证明或许是巧合</p>
<p begin="8559200000t" end="8574200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">不过试想案发当时</p>
<p begin="8574200000t" end="8601900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">亮马先生 晋先生 耕也先生</p>
<p begin="8601900000t" end="8625700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">和音无董事长皆为共犯</p>
<p begin="8625700000t" end="8651400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">一开始就准备好不在场证明</p>
<p begin="8651400000t" end="8679500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">薰子小姐因为没被告知</p>
<p begin="8679500000t" end="8699000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">差点就没有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="8699000000t" end="8729900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">这么解释不是更有意思吗</p>
<p begin="8737400000t" end="8762000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">我对遗产没有兴趣</p>
<p begin="8762000000t" end="8811200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">叔叔们也是判断祖父不会 在遗产分配上刻意刁难</p>
<p begin="8811200000t" end="8859100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">与其亲戚相争 不如采纳你的提议</p>
<p begin="8859100000t" end="8885400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">你却只想看我们笑话吗</p>
<p begin="8892500000t" end="8909200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">真是太没品了</p>
<p begin="8943000000t" end="8978000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">如果包含祖父在内的这4人是共犯</p>
<p begin="8978000000t" end="9003500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">那这次聚会和课题根本就没意义</p>
<p begin="9003500000t" end="9039800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">因为叔叔们都清楚祖父是共犯啊</p>
<p begin="9039800000t" end="9078600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">是的 我并不认为各位是共犯</p>
<p begin="9078600000t" end="9107000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">音无董事长也否定了这个说法</p>
<p begin="9107000000t" end="9125200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">但董事长这么对我说了</p>
<p begin="9125200000t" end="9152000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">犯罪就该遭受报应</p>
<p begin="9170800000t" end="9198300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">爸爸是想要我自白吗</p>
<p begin="9207800000t" end="9228300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">那就是这个课题的目的吗</p>
<p begin="9234100000t" end="9245000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">叔叔?</p>
<p begin="9272500000t" end="9283700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">谁知道呢</p>
<p begin="9283700000t" end="9313400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">毕竟杀人就算只停留在预谋也算犯罪</p>
<p begin="9313400000t" end="9333800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">好吧 我承认</p>
<p begin="9333800000t" end="9360000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">23年前 我和哥哥</p>
<p begin="9360000000t" end="9386300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">一起订定了杀害妈妈的计划</p>
<p begin="9395100000t" end="9406300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">但是还在准备时</p>
<p begin="9406300000t" end="9426900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">妈妈就被不明人士杀死了</p>
<p begin="9426900000t" end="9449800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">所以没有实施计划</p>
<p begin="9449800000t" end="9466900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">跟爸爸一起!?</p>
<p begin="9466900000t" end="9498600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">你们不是已经关系不好30几年了吗</p>
<p begin="9498600000t" end="9516400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">命案当天还打了架…</p>
<p begin="9517000000t" end="9535200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">就是关系不好</p>
<p begin="9535200000t" end="9560800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">才不容易被怀疑是共犯</p>
<p begin="9560800000t" end="9597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">但两人的利害关系基本上是一致的</p>
<p begin="9597000000t" end="9626600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">你果然全都看穿了啊</p>
<p begin="9626600000t" end="9638700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">命案当天</p>
<p begin="9638700000t" end="9676600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">你们两人的争吵激烈到周遭都注意得到</p>
<p begin="9677100000t" end="9700400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">所以才成为有力的不在场证明</p>
<p begin="9700400000t" end="9721200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">但如果你们是共犯</p>
<p begin="9721200000t" end="9741200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">只是做个样子争吵呢?</p>
<p begin="9741200000t" end="9750400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">比方说</p>
<p begin="9750400000t" end="9778800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">在只有你们两人的会议室里吵架</p>
<p begin="9778800000t" end="9811700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">其他人只能从门外听见骚动声音的情况</p>
<p begin="9811700000t" end="9841900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">其中一方的声音是事先录好的</p>
<p begin="9841900000t" end="9859800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">其实房里只有一个人</p>
<p begin="9859800000t" end="9883200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">却演出激烈争吵的样子</p>
<p begin="9883200000t" end="9910700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">就能让大家误以为两人都在房里</p>
<p begin="9910700000t" end="9938200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">不在场的人便能趁这时候去犯案</p>
<p begin="9938200000t" end="9948600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">没错</p>
<p begin="9948600000t" end="9969500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">我们本来是打算这样制造不在场证明</p>
<p begin="9981200000t" end="10020300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">哥哥 特地把我叫来做什么</p>
<p begin="10027500000t" end="10051200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">因为我觉得这件事只能拜托你</p>
<p begin="10051200000t" end="10063700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">这样下去</p>
<p begin="10063700000t" end="10102100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">我们跟集团的未来都会步上灭亡</p>
<p begin="10110000000t" end="10130900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">所以 我要杀掉妈妈</p>
<p begin="10137200000t" end="10167900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">你只要协助我制造不在场证明就好</p>
<p begin="10167900000t" end="10187900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">弄脏手的事就由我来做</p>
<p begin="10196300000t" end="10214200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">所以你已经有计划了是吧</p>
<p begin="10214200000t" end="10244400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">计划大致上跟你说的差不多</p>
<p begin="10244400000t" end="10261500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">但是为了躲避嫌疑</p>
<p begin="10261500000t" end="10278000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">还需要费点功夫</p>
<p begin="10290500000t" end="10299000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">怎么了</p>
<p begin="10299000000t" end="10309400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">打架?</p>
<p begin="10309400000t" end="10344900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">虽然我早就觉得他们两个 最近关系越来越紧张了…</p>
<p begin="10344900000t" end="10363490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">是不是去阻止他们比较好</p>
<p begin="10367700000t" end="10410690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">要让公司内部觉得我和哥哥互殴很正常</p>
<p begin="10410690000t" end="10447100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">即使察觉我们在空房间里吵架</p>
<p begin="10447100000t" end="10465300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">也会选择置之不理</p>
<p begin="10470300000t" end="10497500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">为了营造那种环境才做了事前准备</p>
<p begin="10503300000t" end="10525400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">音无室长 糟糕了</p>
<p begin="10525400000t" end="10535400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">社长她…</p>
<p begin="10541700000t" end="10570000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">结果在妈妈被杀的命案当天</p>
<p begin="10570000000t" end="10598900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">23年前的2月18日时</p>
<p begin="10598900000t" end="10622500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">我们打的那场架成了不在场证明</p>
<p begin="10636400000t" end="10672600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">你们有怀疑过是音无董事长下的手吗</p>
<p begin="10672600000t" end="10705500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">当然 但爸爸有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="10705500000t" end="10731900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">也找不到雇用杀手的证据</p>
<p begin="10731900000t" end="10768500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">所以我们都认为妈妈确实是死于强盗之手</p>
<p begin="10768500000t" end="10790200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">结果事到如今爸爸却提出这个课题</p>
<p begin="10790200000t" end="10807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">我认为如果爸爸不是凶手</p>
<p begin="10807000000t" end="10847000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">那这次就是为了 让我和哥哥自白曾经计划谋杀</p>
<p begin="10847000000t" end="10878600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">并试图要让我们赎罪吧</p>
<p begin="10884200000t" end="10905700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">哥哥应该也察觉到了吧</p>
<p begin="10905700000t" end="10927900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">之所以会派莉音出席</p>
<p begin="10927900000t" end="10951700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">也是想让女儿了解自己的罪行</p>
<p begin="10951700000t" end="10976700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">当作某种形式的赎罪吧</p>
<p begin="10987900000t" end="11036800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">难道叔叔你是为了隐瞒两人的共犯关系</p>
<p begin="11036800000t" end="11066800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">才一直和爸爸装出关系恶劣的样子?</p>
<p begin="11066800000t" end="11082300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">别误会了</p>
<p begin="11082300000t" end="11099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">我是真的很讨厌哥哥</p>
<p begin="11105500000t" end="11129800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">哥哥舍弃了我想做的工作</p>
<p begin="11129800000t" end="11144800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">任性妄为</p>
<p begin="11144800000t" end="11178500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">明明在工作方面比我更优秀</p>
<p begin="11178500000t" end="11208500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">我一直对哥哥抱有自卑感</p>
<p begin="11221600000t" end="11240200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">但我感觉稍微轻松一点了</p>
<p begin="11240200000t" end="11285700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">感谢爸爸准备了这个机会让我自白</p>
<p begin="11285700000t" end="11320300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">那么耕也先生和薰子小姐又是如何</p>
<p begin="11320300000t" end="11358300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">有没有计划过要杀害音无澄女士呢?</p>
<p begin="11358300000t" end="11395400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">薰子小姐受伤的时机实在太巧了</p>
<p begin="11395400000t" end="11426800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">所以我试着推论这是否也是计划好的</p>
<p begin="11426800000t" end="11448900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">薰小姐在命案当天</p>
<p begin="11449300000t" end="11490500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">故意在有人的地方摔倒 假装脚受伤</p>
<p begin="11490500000t" end="11516900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">这时其实根本没骨折</p>
<p begin="11516900000t" end="11543500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">然后在傍晚偷偷溜出公寓</p>
<p begin="11543500000t" end="11577300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">假装成强盗杀害澄女士</p>
<p begin="11577300000t" end="11617000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">之后回到公寓 才自己把脚打断</p>
<p begin="11628100000t" end="11663600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">用这方法假装脚从白天就骨折</p>
<p begin="11663600000t" end="11685300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">让人认为她不可能犯案</p>
<p begin="11685300000t" end="11700700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">亏你能想到</p>
<p begin="11700700000t" end="11737100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">这种光听就觉得脚很疼的方法</p>
<p begin="11737100000t" end="11761700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">但就算她遮着脸</p>
<p begin="11761700000t" end="11790400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">澄女士也不可能把亲生女儿看成男人</p>
<p begin="11790400000t" end="11826800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">从她最后的喊叫能知道犯人是男性</p>
<p begin="11831400000t" end="11871400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">因为她喊的是"抓住穿黑色外套的男人"</p>
<p begin="11871400000t" end="11890500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">最后的那声喊叫</p>
<p begin="11890500000t" end="11914400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">真的是澄女士本人喊的吗</p>
<p begin="11914400000t" end="11948000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">听见叫声的居民并不认得她的声音</p>
<p begin="11948000000t" end="11971500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">如果是为了让人误以为犯人是男性</p>
<p begin="11971500000t" end="11994400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">薰子小姐假装成澄女士</p>
<p begin="11994400000t" end="12030600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">在遗体旁大叫 让别人听到的话呢</p>
<p begin="12030600000t" end="12058600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">这种伪装方式风险也太大了</p>
<p begin="12058600000t" end="12086600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">听见声音的居民立刻跑到路上的话</p>
<p begin="12086600000t" end="12105300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">就会撞见薰子</p>
<p begin="12105300000t" end="12117500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">的确是呢</p>
<p begin="12117500000t" end="12151700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">说到底若是计划在住宅区杀人</p>
<p begin="12151700000t" end="12184200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">应该会设法让被害者发不出声音</p>
<p begin="12184200000t" end="12212200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">并且确认现场没有留下证据</p>
<p begin="12212200000t" end="12240000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">被害者真的断了气才离开吧</p>
<p begin="12249700000t" end="12275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">但是难得有这个机会</p>
<p begin="12275000000t" end="12288900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">就如晋先生所说的</p>
<p begin="12288900000t" end="12310900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">讲出来好像会比较轻松哦</p>
<p begin="12321400000t" end="12343900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">我明白了 我就坦白吧</p>
<p begin="12343900000t" end="12354400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">情况刚好相反</p>
<p begin="12354400000t" end="12391900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">薰子不是为了杀人才骨折</p>
<p begin="12391900000t" end="12403500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">是因为她骨折了</p>
<p begin="12403500000t" end="12426900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">我们的谋杀计划才失败</p>
<p begin="12441500000t" end="12477400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">我和薰子也曾密谋杀害她</p>
<p begin="12485200000t" end="12507000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">选在她从按摩店回家路上这点</p>
<p begin="12507000000t" end="12522800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">和晋先生他们是一样的</p>
<p begin="12522800000t" end="12560700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">因为她只有那时候才会落单</p>
